      "name": "Spherity European Business Wallet",
      "description": "Spherity’s European Business Wallet (EBW) enables the seamless exchange of verifiable credentials across organisations, from banking, insurance and beyond. As part of the EBW framework and fully eIDAS 2.0-compliant, it streamlines operations, cuts costs, and boosts efficiency. Enhanced with automated business partner data validation, our Business Wallet transforms how businesses handles regulatory obligations in Germany and beyond. With enterprise-grade data automation and primary source-validated information from Bundesanzeiger Verlag, businesses can minimise risks, eliminate manual KYC/KYS processes, and ensure real-time due diligence. Organisations operating in regulated industries or managing complex supply chains, our solution helps you meet obligations such as Anti-Money Laundering regulations.",
